item.title: CVE-2024-10332|2024-10-24T13:42:19.261Z -- janto -- janto
item.description: A Cross-Site Scripting vulnerability has been found in Janto v4.3r11 from Impronta. This vulnerability allows an attacker to execute JavaScript code in the victim's browser by sending the victim a malicious URL using the endpoint “/abonados/public/janto/main.php”.
